{"tid":2159512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"對TikTok再補刀！川普在競爭對手Triller開帳號","createTime":"2020-08-16T11:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:17:22.000Z","uid":75656,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a03c94a74bf845efba6d83fd3d83d0d8ab7cc3bc","tid":2159512,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普對中國短影音平台TikTok的厭惡表露無疑，外媒15日報導，川普現在已擁有TikTok競爭對手Triller的認證帳號，這成為TikTok遭到白宮厭棄的又1個跡象。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，TikTok深受美國青少年喜愛，但因具中資背景，美國官員擔心用戶資訊可能被提交給中國政府。而在川普本月下達對TikTok的禁令後，TikTok的同類手機應用程式下載量激增，其中就包括Triller。<br />\n<br />\n截至15日晚間，川普已在Triller上張貼3則短影音，並擁有3000多名粉絲。川普競選連任團隊與Triller目前都未回覆《路透》的詢問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3261974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3261974&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=154885da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3261974&h=ea035658\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3261974</a>"},{"pid":"a69d1189a6ab58859621f2b3b2dd4b0a9ba42f00","tid":2159512,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0208c9dff9e0c54179b2ca9821c8100f3a49871f","tid":2159512,"uid":54622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"2fe52d1c3c4e01a3d3acb9b10751d740ebcafc6e","tid":2159512,"uid":62950,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"香港人係咪應該點都開個黎玩下 當twitter睇下野都好"},{"pid":"2f87b781b7033e55229c34602e8385d9724880d2","tid":2159512,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9899783cd8fd9334d3b3059943e7099f81e6cf79","tid":2159512,"uid":44209,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2fe52d1c3c4e01a3d3acb9b10751d740ebcafc6e","tid":21595